<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/aug/20/">&#x27a0;</a> August 20, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="even-office-2007-box-has-learn" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.joelonsoftware.com/items/2007/08/18.html">Even the Office 2007 box has a learning curve - Joel on Software</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>As someone who installed Vista on a PC in January, and regretted it for months, I echo Joel Spolsky&#8217;s summation: &#8220;I&#8217;ve been using Vista on my home laptop since it shipped, and can say with some conviction that nobody should be using it as their primary operating system &#8212; it simply has no redeeming merits to overcome the compatibility headaches it causes.&#8221;</p>

