    <div class="well" id="very-slow-internet-browsing-vi" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.vistax64.com/vista-performance-maintenance/19228-very-slow-internet-browsing.html">Very slow internet browsing - Vista x64 Forums</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>&#8220;netsh int tcp set global autotuninglevel=disabled&#8221; &#8212; The magic incantation that stops network performance SUCKING BALLS (at least on the RhymesWithNose network) in Vista.</p>

