    <div class="well" id="windows-media-player-firefox" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://port25.technet.com/pages/windows-media-player-firefox-plugin-download.aspx">Port 25 : Windows Media Player Firefox Plugin - Download</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>From the &#8220;about bloody time&#8221; file, a plugin from Microsoft for Firefox which allows WMV files to stream in your browser.  This has been broken (and required lots of DLL copying) for years.</p>

